{{aimai}}
{{デフォルトソート:りくふ}}

**Rikubu / Rokubu** (六部)  

- **Rikubu** (りくぶ) – A general term for the six government ministries that managed administration in the central government of China from the Sui to Qing dynasties. ⇒ {{ill|Three Departments and Six Ministries|ja|三省六部}}  
- **Rokubu** (ろくぶ) – An abbreviation for {{ill|Sixty-Six Pilgrimage Monks|ja|六十六部}}, referring to itinerant Buddhist monks on pilgrimage.  

{{aimai}}  

